  "title": "NEW! Finance and Business Manager",
  "description": "<ul><li>Manage office and project finance operations, including budgeting, accounting, reporting, financial planning, and cost control.</li><li>Ensure compliance with financial policies, tax and regulatory requirements, maintaining accurate project records in systems such as SAP.</li><li>Provide commercial support across projects, including contract and claims management, risk and opportunity assessment, and productivity initiatives.</li><li>Partner with the Business Administration Manager to uphold governance standards, ethical conduct, and a strong culture of integrity across the team.</li></ul><p>Interested applicants please send your resume in MS Word format and attention it to Rachel Yeo (R22104385).<br />Shortlisted candidates will be notified<br />Data provided is for recruitment purposes only<br />www.ambition.com.sg<br />EA Registration Number: R22104385<br />Business Registration Number: 200611680D. Licence Number: 10C5117</p>",
